<LP>
   MINORCO (USA) -- Robert L. Zerga was named chairman and
chief executive officer of Independence Mining Co., a Reno,
Nev., gold-mining unit. He was also named a director of
Denver-based Minorco (USA). Mr. Zerga was executive vice
president of Meridian Minerals Co., a unit of Burlington
Resources Inc. He was previously with Newmont Gold Co., Magma
Copper Co. and Kennecott Copper Corp.
